\c 11
\p
\v 1 Iniwo mugore rekutanga raDhariyasi muMedhiya, ndakasimuka kusimbisa nekumutsigira.
\s Hondo dzeVaPeresia neVaGiriki
\p
\v 2 Ikozvino ndava kuzokuudza chokwadi. Tarira, kuchamira amwe madzimambo matatu muPeresia; uye wechina achava mupfumi kupfuura vese; uye nesimba rake kubudikidza neufumi uzhinji achamutsa vese kupikisa umambo hweGirisi.
\v 3 Zvino mambo ane simba achamira, uye achatonga nekutonga kukuru, nekuita zvinoenderana nechido chake.
\v 4 Zvino paachasimuka, umambo hwake huchagurwa, uye huchaparadzanisirwa kumhepo ina dzekumatenga, uye kwete kuti abudirire, uye zvisingaenderani nekutonga kwake kwaakatonga, nokuti umambo hwake huchadzurirwa vamwe kunze kweava.
\p
\v 5 Zvino mambo wekuchamhembe achava nesimba, ne\add umwe\add* wemachinda ake; zvino \add iye\add* achava nesimba kumupfuura, zvino achatonga, kutonga kwake kuchava kutonga kukuru.
\v 6 Zvino pakupera kwemakore, vachabatana, nokuti mukunda wamambo wekuchamhembe achaenda kuna mambo wekumaodzanyemba kunoita sungano yakaenzaniswa, asi haangarambi akabata simba reruoko; uye haangamiri, kana ruoko rwake, asi achapiwa, nevakamuunza, newakamubereka, newakamusimbisa panguva idzi.
\v 7 Asi kuchasimuka \add umwe\add* kubva padavi remidzi yake pachinzvimbo chake; iye achauya nehondo, uye achapinda munhare dzamambo wekumaodzanyemba, uye achabata nekuvarwisa ndokukunda.
\v 8 Nevamwari vavo pamwe nemachinda avo pamwe nemidziyo yavo inokosha yesirivha neyegoridhe achatapira kuEgipita, uye achaenderera kweamwe makore kupfuura mambo wekumaodzanyemba.
\v 9 Naizvozvo mambo wekuchamhembe achapinda paumambo ndokudzokera kunyika yake.
\p
\v 10 Asi mwanakomana wake achavamutsa, uye achaunganidza chaunga chevarwi vakuru. Zvino vachauya zvirokwazvo, ndokufashamira, ndokupfuura, ipapo achadzoka ndokubvongodzwa, kusvika kunhare yake.
\v 11 Zvino mambo wekuchamhembe achatsamwa zvikuru, ndokubuda ndokurwa naye, namambo wekumaodzanyemba; asi chaunga ichi chichapiwa muruoko rwake.
\v 12 Chaunga chichinge chabviswa, moyo wake uchazvikudza, uye achawisra pasi vane makumi ezvuru, asi haangavi nesimba.
\v 13 Nokuti mambo wekumaodzanyemba achadzoka, zvino achamisa chaunga chakakura kudarika chekutanga, uye achauya zvirokwazvo pakupera kwenguva dzemakore, achasvika zvirokwazvo ane hondo huru nenhumbi zhinji.
\p
\v 14 Zvino panguva idzodzo kuchasimuka vazhinji kurwisa mambo wekuchamhembe; uye vane hasha vevanhu vako vachazvikudza kuti vasimbise chiratidzo, asi vachagumburwa.
\v 15 Naizvozvo mambo wekumaodzanyemba achasvika, ndokuvatutira murwi, ndokutapa maguta akashoshewa kwazvo; uye maoko ekuchamhembe haangamiri, nevakasarudzwa vake, uye hakungavi nesimba rekumirandzingagoni kumira, kunyange navanhu vake vakatsaurwa, uye vachashayiwa simba rokumira naro.
\v 16 Asi uyo anouya kuzorwa naye achaita sezvaanoda, hakuna angamira pamberi pake; zvino iye achamira panyika yakaisvonaka, akabata kuparadza muruoko rwake.
\v 17 Ipapo achashingaira kuuya nesimba roushe hwake hwese, ane sungano yake; achaita izvozvo, achamupa mwanasikana wavakadzi, kuti amuparadze; asi zvichakona, haana chaachawana.
\v 18 Shure kwaizvozvo acharinzira chiso chake kuzvivi, ndokukunda zvizhinji; asi umwe mukuru wehondo achagumisa kushoora kwake; kunze kokuti achadzosera kushoora kwake kuna iye amene.
\v 19 Ipapo acharinzira chiso chake kunhare dzenyika yake; asi achagumburwa nokuwa, ndokushayikwa.
\p
\v 20 Zvino panzvimbo yake kuchamuka umwe achatuma muteresi kupfuura pakaisvonaka paushe hwake, asi kana mazuva mashoma apera uchaparadzwa, zvisingaitwi nehasha kana nokurwa.
\v 21 Panzvimbo yake kuchamuka munhu anofanira kuzvidzwa, akange asina kupiwa kukudzwa koushe; asi iye achasvika nenguva yokufara kwavanhu, ndokutora ushe nokubata kumeso.
\v 22 Hondo dzinokukura dzichakukurwa pamberi pake, dzichaparadzwa; zvirokwazvo, naiye muchinda wesunganowo.
\v 23 Kana apedza kusungana navo, achavanyengera; nokuti achakwirira, nokuva nesimba navanhu vashoma.
\v 24 Nenguva yokufara kwavanhu achapinda pamativi akaorera enyika; achaita zvisina kumboitwa namadzibaba ake, kunyange namadzibaba amadzibaba ake; achaparadzira pakati pavo zvaakatapa nezvaakapamba nenhumbi; achatanda mano ake pamusoro penhare, asi nenguva chete.
\v 25 Ipapo achamutsira mambo wezasi simba rake nomwoyo wake, ane hondo huru kwazvo ine simba; asi haangamiri, nokuti vachamutandira mano.
\v 26 Vanodya zvokudya zvake, ndivo vachamuparadza; hondo yake ichapararira, vazhinji vachawira pasi vaurawa.
\v 27 Kana ari madzimambo awo maviri, mwoyo yavo ichada kuita zvakashata, vachareva nhema vari patafura rimwe; asi hazvingabatsiri, nokuti kuguma kuchasvika nenguva yakatarwa.
\v 28 Ipapo achadzokera kunyika yake nenhumbi zhinji; mwoyo wake uchavenga sungano, achaita sezvaanoda, ndokudzokera kunyika yake.
\p
\v 29 Nenguva yakatarwa uchadzoka, ndokusvika kunyika yechamhembe; asi nenguva yokupedzisira hazvingaiti sapakutanga.
\v 30 Nokuti zvikepe zveKitimi zvichauya kuzorwa naye; naizvozvo achaora mwoyo, ndokudzoka akatsamwa pamusoro pesungano, ndokuita sezvaanoda; achadzoka, ndokuva nehanya navakaramba sungano tsvene.
\v 31 Hondo dzichamutswa naye, dzichamhura nzvimbo tsvene, iye nhare, vachabvisa chipo chinopiswa nguva dzese, ndokumutsa chinonyangadza chinoparadza.
\v 32 Vanoitira sungano zvakaipa, achavatsausa nokubata kumeso; asi vanhu vanoziva Mwari wavo, vachava nesimba, vachaita mabasa makuru.
\v 33 Vakachenjera pakati pavanhu vachadzidzisa vazhinji; asi vachaparadzwa nomunondo, uye nemurazvo womoto, uye nokutapwa, uye nokupambiwa mazuva mazhinji.
\v 34 Zvino kana voparadzwa vachabatsirwa nokubatsirwa kudiki; asi vazhinji vachazviisa kwavari nokubata kumeso.
\v 35 Vamwe vavo vakachenjera vachaparadzwa, kuti vaedzwe, vacheneswe, kusvikira kunguva yokupedzisira; nokuti nguva yokupedzisira ichigere kusvika.
\p
\v 36 Mambo uyo achaita sezvaanoda; achazviita mukuru, achazvikudza achiti ndinopfuura vamwari vese, achataura zvinhu zvinoshamisa pamusoro paMwari wavamwari; iye achafara pane zvaanoita kusvikira kutsamwa kwapera, nokuti zvakatemwa zvichaitika.
\v 37 Uye haangavi nehanya navamwari vamadzibaba ake, kana norudo rwavakadzi, haangavi nehanya namwari upi noupi; nokuti achazvikudza achiti ndakapfuura vese.
\v 38 Asi panzvimbo yazvo achakudza mwari wenhare; mwari wakange asingazikamwi namadzibaba ake, ndiye waachakudza negoridhe nesirivha namabwe anokosha nezvinhu zvinodikanwa.
\v 39 Acharwa nenhare dzakaisvobata achibatsirwa namwari wavatorwa; ani nani waanorangarira, iye achakudzwa naye zvikuru; achavabatisa ushe pamusoro pavanhu vazhinji, achivagovera nyika uve mubairo wavo.
\p
\v 40 Zvino nenguva yokupedzisira mambo wechamhembe achapesana naye; mambo wokumaodzanyemba achauya kuzorwa naye sechamupupuri, ane ngoro navatasvi vamabhiza nezvikepe zvizhinji, achapinda munyika idzo, ndokupararira, ndokupfuura neseri.
\v 41 Achapindawo munyika yakaisvonaka, nyika zhinji dzichakundwa, asi idzi dzicharwirwa paruoko rwake, dzinoti Edhomu, neMoabhu norutivi rwakanaka rwavana vaAmoni.
\v 42 Achatambanudzirawo ruoko rwake kune dzimwe nyika; nyika yeEgipita haingapukunyuki.
\v 43 Asi achava anesimba pamusoro pefuma yegoridhe nesirivha, napamusoro pezvinhu zvese zvinokosha zveEgipita; vaRibhia navaItiyopiya vachatevera makwara ake.
\v 44 Asi mashoko anobva kumabvazuva nokumaodzanyemba achamuvhundusa; ipapo achabuda nehasha kwazvo kundoparadza nokupedza chese vazhinji.
\v 45 Achadzika matende ake oushe pakati pemakungwa negomo dzvene rakaisvonaka; kunyange zvakadaro achasvika pakuguma kwake, achashayiwa anomubatsira.
